13:["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-10","children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl sm:text-2xl font-bold text-foreground mb-4","children":"Kalkulyatordan qanday foydalanish"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"prose prose-sm sm:prose-base max-w-none text-muted-foreground space-y-4","children":[["$","div","0",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Kalkulyator qanday ishlaydi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Marja kalkulyatori biznes rentabelligining asosiy ko'rsatkichlarini hisoblaydi: marja (sotish narxi va tannarx orasidagi farq), marjinallik (tushumdagi marja ulushi) va ustama (tannarxdagi marja ulushi). Bu ko'rsatkichlar O'zbekistondagi har bir tadbirkorga narx belgilash, rentabellik tahlili va boshqaruv qarorlarini qabul qilish uchun zarur."}]]}]]}],["$","div","1",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash formulasi"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Hisoblash formulalari: Marja = Sotish narxi − Tannarx. Marjinallik = (Marja / Sotish narxi) × 100%. Ustama = (Marja / Tannarx) × 100%. Bu tushunchalarni farqlash muhim: marjinallik doimo 100% dan kam, ustama esa istalgan qiymatda bo'lishi mumkin. Masalan, tannarx 500 000, narx 800 000 so'mda marja 300 000, marjinallik — 37,5%, ustama — 60% bo'ladi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","2",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Hisoblash misoli"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistonda tarmoqlar bo'yicha o'rtacha marjinallik: oziq-ovqat chakana savdosi — 15-25%, kiyim-kechak — 30-50%, umumiy ovqatlanish — 40-65%, IT-xizmatlar — 50-70%, qurilish materiallari — 20-35%. Tarmoq me'yorlarini bilish biznesingiz raqobatbardoshligini va rentabellikni oshirish zaxiralarini tushunishga yordam beradi."}]]}]]}],["$","div","3",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Nimalarni hisobga olish kerak"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"O'zbekistondagi kichik biznes va yakka tartibdagi tadbirkorlar uchun marja kalkulyatori kundalik vosita hisoblanadi. Toshkentdagi «Abu Sahiy» yoki «Ippodrom» ulgurji bozoridan tovar sotib olayotganda, ijara, sotuvchilar ish haqi, soliqlar (soddalashtilgan tizimda YaTT uchun 4%) va kerakli foydani qoplash uchun ustamani oldindan hisoblash muhim."}]]}]]}],["$","div","4",{"children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mt-6 mb-2","children":"Foydali maslahatlar"}],["$","p",null,{"className":"leading-relaxed","children":[["$","$1","0",{"children":"Kalkulyator ikki rejimda ishlaydi: to'g'ridan-to'g'ri hisoblash (tannarx va sotish narxidan marjaga) va teskari hisoblash (kerakli marjinallikdan zarur sotish narxiga). Ikkinchi rejim narxlar ro'yxatini shakllantirishda ayniqsa qulay: tannarxni va maqsadli 30% marjinallikni kiriting — kalkulyator minimal sotish narxini ko'rsatadi. Bu barqaror narx siyosatini shakllantirishga yordam beradi."}]]}]]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mt-8 space-y-6","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg sm:text-xl font-semibold text-foreground","children":"Ma'lumotnoma va tariflar"}],[["$","div","0",{"className":"overflow-x-auto rounded-xl border border-border","children":["$","table",null,{"className":"w-full text-sm","children":[["$","caption",null,{"className":"px-4 py-2 text-left font-medium text-foreground bg-muted/50 border-b border-border","children":"Biznes uchun soliq rejimlarini taqqoslash"}],["$","thead",null,{"children":"$L19"}],"$L1a"]}]}]]]}],"$L1b","$L1c"]}]
